	MUDF ointment is designed to use on your horse or pony on and around the hoof. To use, apply the natural ointment above the hoof where it meets the skin, back pastern and heels twice per day to aid clearing. If the condition is present dry the area as often as possible and remove any wet, matted hair. If not present, dry the feet off whenever possible and apply the ointment as above before the animal goes back out. This is a large 200ml tub for only &pound;9.99.</p>
